Event handlers  In order to keep the Opentelemetry context within your event handlers, you need to wrap your own with   defineTracedHandler  from   nitro-opentelemetry/runtime/utils :     // this is also auto-imported
 import   { defineTracedEventHandler }   from   "nitro-opentelemetry/runtime/utils"

 export   default   defineTracedEventHandler  (()   =>   {
     return   "Hello World !"
 })
